OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother day of long sunny
OL,6,Fspells, though rather breezy once
OL,7,Fagain, with the strongest winds near
OL,8,Fcoasts and across hills. Warm inland
OL,9,Fbut cooler along the coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine evening leading into a
OL,12,Fdry and chilly night with long clear
OL,13,Fspells. Brisk winds near coasts easing
OL,14,Fthrough the night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FFriday, starting chilly then
OL,17,Fmostly fine through the day and
OL,18,Fturning very warm by afternoon. Chance
OL,19,Fof cloud bringing showers later,
OL,20,Fmainly across the Derbyshire Hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
