OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,6,FCloudier over the weekend and into
OL,7,FMonday with an increased chance of
OL,8,Frain or showers, perhaps thundery.
OL,9,FTemperatures returning to near normal
OL,10,Fwith generally light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
